      "text": "You bring me thread and needle, I'm going to sew you the nicest thing what you want.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And also, if you bring me some, I will cook you the best thing, what you want.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just leave Magda, because in a few days she will be all right.",
